		"description": "The definitive, production-ready Postman collection for SetuGeo. Includes recursive geographic drills, advanced banking analytics, equity intelligence, and geospatial clustering.\n\n**Production URL:** https://setugeo.com/api/v1\n**OCR API:** https://api.setugeo.com\n**Local Development:** http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1",
